  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Safe Spaces for Children Impacted by Peru Floods</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Flooding has been plaguing Peru since December causing massive destruction. We have officially launched a response program to focus on cleaning out affected schools, constructing temporary learning centers, mobilizing local volunteers, and mucking out homes. Over 1,000 children have been displaced from their learning spaces and our volunteers will work to clean out those schools and construct temporary learning centers so children can gain back some normalcy.</narrative>
  </description>
